Movie Description
Three youths while hiking in Finland, happen on a barbed wire fence marking the border with the Soviet Union and decide to sneak across as a prank. They get caught and accused of murder, subjected to brutal interrogation, forced to confess as spies and imprisoned.

Credits 
Cast: David Coburn, Mike Norris, Steve Durham 
Director: Renny Harlin
